# Design system

- Never hardcode a colour, font, spacing, radius, or transition value.
- Always use tokens from `css/tokens.css`.
- If a token doesn't exist for what you need, add it to `tokens.css` first, then reference it.
- Font pairing: Lora (display/headings) + IBM Plex Sans (body/UI).
- Primary accent: --color-accent (#185FA5).
- Design reference: Lora + IBM Plex Sans, clean editorial style, not corporate.